# Development Philosophy

Avoid:

* giant prompt injection
* monolithic context windows
* LLM-managed memory
* infinite reflection loops
* tightly coupled orchestration

Prefer:

* deterministic runtime execution
* scoped cognition
* reference-based memory
* event-driven systems
* modular architecture

