# Vision

The long-term vision is not:

* smarter prompts

but:

* runtime-managed cognition systems
* persistent semantic execution
* scalable AI operating runtimes
* low-resource autonomous agents
* reloaded model when over context or overthinking

This project explores what happens when:

* the runtime owns cognition
* and the LLM becomes a semantic coprocessor.

# Design Goals

* Long-running AI agents
* Local AI support
* Low VRAM usage
* Modular orchestration
* Persistent cognition
* Event-driven execution
* Reference-based memory
* Scalable worker systems
* Runtime-managed reasoning

